## Statistical Test

Paired tests were run across the same seeds, comparing `test_at_best_valid`.

| test | p-value |
| --- | ---: |
| paired t-test, two-sided | 0.5013 |
| paired t-test, one-sided GSMP > GCN | 0.2506 |
| Wilcoxon signed-rank, two-sided | 0.7500 |
| Wilcoxon signed-rank, one-sided GSMP > GCN | 0.3750 |

Conclusion: the 100-epoch 3-seed result is not statistically significant at `p < 0.05`. It shows a small positive trend for GSMP, but the evidence is weak with only 3 seeds.

